    twitterColor: 'hsl(203, 89%, 53%)',
    instagramColor: 'pink',
    youtubeColor: 'hsl(348, 97%, 39%)',
    bgToggle: {

      100: '#b6f5e4',

      300: '#62e6c2',
      400: '#39dfb0',
